Package rocks.palaiologos.maja.expression

Interface ExpressionListener

All Superinterfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
public interface ExpressionListener extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by ExpressionParser.
